Weegunetapkei ne po Israel ak Judah


1  Ki nyoonji Jeremiah `ng'olyoot ne ki punu Kamuktaindet ne Toroor, koleenji 
2  mwaei Kamuktaindet ne Toroor, Kamuktaindetap Israel, kole, sirchi bukuit ng'aleek tugul che koamwaun. 
3  Keero, pwoonei peetuusyek, mwaei Kamuktaindet ne Toroor, che awale luuleetap piikyuk Israel ak Judah, mwaei Kamuktaindet ne Toroor: ak agoochi icheek koweek kobwa emet ne ki agoochi kwanisyekwak, ak kobunji.


4  Ak chu ng'aleek che ki mwa Kamuktaindet ne Toroor agobo Israel ak Judah. 
5  Amu mwaei Kamuktaindet ne Toroor kole: Kigegas tuugeet ne po potanet, ak ne po kaiyweisyet, ne ma po kaalyeet. 
6  Oteep anyun, si onai ngo tinyei mureno ng'wanindo ne po sigisyet: amu nee anyun si ageere muren age tugul konamei suennyi, ko uu kwondo ne machei kosigiis, ak kowalogis togoochik tugul eng' arageneet? 
7  Pwo eng' peetuunooto, peetuut ne oo ne ma mi ne kergei: peetuutap nyalilda eng' Jakobo; nga kisaru eng' nyalilato.


8  Ak tuun airie eng' peetuunooto choginnyi ne mi kaating'ung', mwaei Kamuktaindet ne Toroor ne po lugoosyek, ak ang'etii anooguk; ama koyaei toek ineendet koek otwogindennywa. 
9  Ago otei Kamuktaindet ne Toroor Kamuktaindennywa, ak Daudi laitoryannywa, ne ang'eetyini icheek.


10   Meiywei anyun, ee Jakobo otwogindennyu, mwaei Kamuktaindet ne Toroor; ametoptoben, ee Israel: amu asaruun eng' ole loo, kobooto iyoteng'ung', komong' eng' emet ne kiga kiluulji; ak koweek Jakobo, ak kosiis, ak komuuny, ama komi chii ne imui ineendet. 
11  Amu ami kobooten, mwaei Kamuktaindet ne Toroor, si asaruun; amu ageesu pororyosyek tugul che kigayestochin, ago magesun inyee; ago atigoonenen kirwooget, amabagaaktoin ama kibirin. 
12  Amu mwaei Kamuktaindet ne Toroor kole, ma inyaaksei kaguoteneng'ung', ak ko ng'waan moeng'ung'. 
13  Ma mi chii ne ng'alaaldaun, si kobiit kinyain: metinye kerichek che kinyaise. 
14  Kigoutyenen chamaniguk tugul: ma cheeng'in: amu kaaguotenin eng' kaguotenetap puunyoot eng' katigonetap ineendet ne koroom; amu ooindap yaityeng'ung', amu kitesagis tengekwogiguk. 
15  Amu nee si iriir eng' kaguoteneng'ung'? Ma inyaaksei ng'wanindang'ung'. Koayaun anyun tuguuchuuto, amu ooindap yaityeng'ung', ak amu kitesagis tengekwogiguk. 
16  Ki amei anyun icheek tugul che amin; kiluulei puuniguk tugul, wendi age tugul luuleet; ak kiluulei icheek tugul che luulin, ak agoitoi kebar icheek che cheeng'ei kobarin. 
17  Amu asaabin, ak anyaa mooguk, mwaei Kamuktaindet ne Toroor; amu kigoguurenen ne ki kitimda, kole Zion niito, ne ma mage kiy chii. 
18  Mwaei Kamuktaindet ne Toroor kole, ogeero, awale kogeny luuleetap emaisyegap Jakobo, ak ariiree meng'otosyekyik; ak keteech nganaseet karaitanyi, ak kotebi kootap laitoryat ko uu yeginye. 
19  Ak komang'une olooto kongoi ak kutitap icheeget che igasegei: ak ates icheek, ama kong'ering'itu; atoroori kogeny icheek, ama konyeratitu. 
20  Ak koigei lagokwak atkinye tai, ak kogimit tuiyennywa eng' tainnyu, ak abir tugul che usei icheek. 
21  Ak kobiitune icheek pounindennywa, ak komang'une kwenunnywa kirwoogindennywa; ak agoochini ineendet koriik, konyo koriikyo; amu ng'oo ineendet ne tinyei nyiganateet koriikyo? Mwaei Kamuktaindet ne Toroor. 
22  Ak oegu piikyuk, ak aegu Kamuktaindeng'wong'. 
23  Ogeero, kagomong' kipchurchuryetap Kamuktaindet ne Toroor, nooto ko nereeknatennyi ne koroom, ee kipchurchuryet ne usei kot: kwerei metowegap kiptengeginik. 
24  Ma weeksei nereegek che ng'woneen che po Kamuktaindet ne Toroor agoi koyai kogees, agoi koyai magutigap muguleldanyi kosulda: oguitosi ng'olyoondoniito eng' peetuusyek che po let.

